        <div class="cb-admin-section-title">Global settings bölümleri</div>
        <p class="cb-admin-section-description">Canlı snapshot, kritik aksiyon ve düşük öncelikli varsayılan bloklar ayrı tutulur; kullanıcı ayarları ile karışmaz.</p>

        <div class="cb-admin-settings-nav mt-5">
            <a class="cb-admin-settings-nav-link is-active" href="#cb_admin_settings_live_snapshot">Canlı Snapshot</a>
            <a class="cb-admin-settings-nav-link" href="#cb_admin_settings_controls">Kritik Kontroller</a>
            <a class="cb-admin-settings-nav-link cb-admin-settings-nav-link-danger" href="#cb_admin_settings_execution">Execution Hard Gate</a>
            <a class="cb-admin-settings-nav-link" href="#cb_admin_settings_global_state">Global System State</a>
            <a class="cb-admin-settings-nav-link" href="#cb_admin_settings_clock_sync">Runtime Sync Ops</a>
            <a class="cb-admin-settings-nav-link cb-admin-settings-nav-link-danger" href="#cb_admin_settings_crisis">Crisis Escalation</a>
            <a class="cb-admin-settings-nav-link" href="#cb_admin_settings_logging">Logging / Retention</a>
            <a class="cb-admin-settings-nav-link" href="#cb_admin_settings_risk">Risk / Policy Engine</a>
        </div>

        <div class="cb-admin-info-strip cb-admin-info-strip-warning mt-6">
            <div>
                <div class="cb-admin-info-strip-title">Critical command envelope</div>
